message: "These crimes occur largely in the shadows, outside of public view, but this victim escaped and thanks to a concerned motorist and the swift response of the NJSP and partnering agencies, she was rescued and her traffickers were successfully prosecuted. This case should motivate other members of the public to alert authorities when they suspect human trafficking.” #NJSP #MakingADifference https://buff.ly/36eMgZL
